  "description": "Redevelopment and change of use of existing filling station (sui generis) involving the demolition of existing pump islands, canopy, laundrette building and infill underground tanks, to facilitate the creation of an electric vehicle charging hub (sui generis) including ten bays with charging posts, substation and associated infrastructure",
